author: Lauren Murphy
title: MusicNews | Janet Jackson announces gig at Dublin's 3Arena
text:
Janet Jackson is embarking on a world tour to promote her new album 'Unbreakable', and Irish fans will be delighted to know that she plans a stop-off in Dublin along the way.
The pop star will play Dublin's 3Arena on April 2nd, 2016.
Tickets are from â‚¬42.55 including booking fee, and on sale from usual outlets this Friday at 10am.
